headline: 2 No-Brainer High Yield Utility Stocks to Buy Right Now
summary: Utilities are set to see an increase in demand thanks to AI, data centers, and EVs.  Dominion Energy is a turnaround story, but one that is relatively low risk and relatively high yield.  Black Hills is a Dividend King with a notably above-average yield.
